-- European Coal for Next Year Delivery Advances for Third Day
-- B y   M a r e k   S t r z e l e c k i
-- 2012-10-08T14:29:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-08/european-coal-for-next-year-delivery-advances-for-third-day.html
European coal for 2013 advanced for a
third day, reversing early declines.  Thermal coal for delivery next year to Amsterdam, Rotterdam
or Antwerp added 0.2 percent to $97.35 a metric ton at 3:10 p.m.
in  London , according to broker data compiled by Bloomberg.  Bloomberg tracks information supplied by ICAP Plc, GFI
Group Inc., Spectron Group Ltd., Credit Suisse Group AG, IHS
McCloskey, Tradition Financial Services and Tullett Prebon Plc.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marek Strzelecki in Warsaw at 
